the demo for the new song came in.

65
00:04:08,760 --> 00:04:09,530
Huh?

66
00:04:11,570 --> 00:04:14,280
We're going to postpone sales.

67
00:04:14,500 --> 00:04:17,330
Hey! Why?! Why is this happening?!

68
00:04:17,870 --> 00:04:20,020
We don't have a song written.
It can't be helped.

69
00:04:18,220 --> 00:04:24,310
[Ichi Terakado (Otsu's mother and manager)]

70
00:04:20,790 --> 00:04:23,880
