song because of a crazy reason like that.

82
00:04:50,800 --> 00:04:51,890
Anyway...

83
00:04:51,890 --> 00:04:53,000
"I was playing my shamisen,

84
00:04:53,000 --> 00:04:56,410
when a man with naturally
wavy hair hit my helicopter

