about playing a shamisen

94
00:05:19,150 --> 00:05:22,360
and his helicopter crashing
into the ground...

95
00:05:23,700 --> 00:05:25,520
There's no way he'd only have
suffered a sprained finger.

96
00:05:25,520 --> 00:05:27,150
Is that all you care about, Mom?!

97
00:05:27,980 --> 00:05:29,840
There was a good deal of conflict

98
00:05:29,840 --> 00:05:32,210
at the last-minute meeting about
postponing Otsu's new single.

99
00:05:32,570 --> 00:05:34,780
We asked everyone for their thoughts

100
00:05:34,780 --> 00:05:35,990
about Tsunpo, the producer...

101
00:05:35,990 --> 00:05:37,800
and the cause of this problem.

102
00:05:36,890 --> 00:05:54,810
[Q: What kind of person is Tsunpo?]

103
00:05:38,290 --> 00:05:40,010
Huh? Tsunpo-san?

104
00:05:40,200 --> 00:05:42,030
He's an amazing guy.

105
00:05:42,710 --> 00:05:46,270
His bold, yet delicate, skills keep
others from getting near him and

106
