112
00:06:04,350 --> 00:06:05,560
[Q: That really bothers you, doesn't it?]

113
00:06:05,560 --> 00:06:09,270
[Q: What do you think about Tsunpo-san?]

114
00:06:05,980 --> 00:06:09,200
I think it's important to know
whether he's edible or not.

115
00:06:09,530 --> 00:06:12,470
