really sold, anyway...

121
00:06:31,810 --> 00:06:33,220
Shut your face...

122
00:06:33,880 --> 00:06:36,980
Shut up and bring me
Akimoto or Mackey...

123
00:06:33,880 --> 00:06:36,980
[Note: Yasushi Akimoto and Mackey (Noriyuki Makihara)
are Japanese songwriters and producers.]

124
00:06:37,930 --> 00:06:40,120
Anyway, do you even want to do this?

125
