156
00:08:06,430 --> 00:08:09,540
I was spoiled by my situation.

157
00:08:10,060 --> 00:08:12,020
I have to go to a place where no one

158
00:08:12,020 --> 00:08:15,560
knows who I am, reexamine myself,

159
00:08:15,790 --> 00:08:18,060
and get back the feelings I lost.

160
00:08:21,650 --> 00:08:23,450
Nakata went on a trip to find himself.

161
00:08:21,650 --> 00:08:25,600
[Note: Hide Nakata is a Japanese soccer player.]

162
00:08:23,450 --> 00:08:25,600
I must do that, too...

163
00:08:26,960 --> 00:08:30,160
Ah... This is heaven...

164
00:08:30,060 --> 00:08:32,930
