207
00:10:35,570 --> 00:10:40,880
I can't make it… I really am no good.

208
00:10:41,570 --> 00:10:45,800
I can't do anything by myself.
I'm a manufactured pop idol.

209
00:10:46,450 --> 00:10:48,790
