229
00:11:57,880 --> 00:11:59,740
Now I’ve done it…

230
00:12:00,260 --> 00:12:02,130
I've done it again…

231
00:12:02,540 --> 00:12:03,590
Makoto-chan!

232
00:12:05,840 --> 00:12:07,390
And Corpse-chan!!

233
00:12:07,390 --> 00:12:08,770
Huh? Come to think of it,
where's the Captain?

234
00:12:09,370 --> 00:12:10,960
You're right. He's not here.

235
00:12:12,020 --> 00:12:15,410
It's not a bad thing to be stubborn
and stick it out on your own.

236
00:12:16,540 --> 00:12:18,130
But you're not alone.

237
00:12:19,760 --> 00:12:23,540
Otsu, everyone's gathered
here for your sake.

238
00:12:24,280 --> 00:12:25,960
In order to help you…

239
00:12:27,320 --> 00:12:32,260
Yes. Tsu Terakado is supported
by all these people.

240
00:12:34,640 --> 00:12:37,940
Have confidence. Everyone supports you.

241
00:12:38,300 --> 00:12:40,440
There's still time until the release!

242
00:12:40,670 --> 00:12:41,630
We'll help you!!

